<P>
   ZIMBABWE-ELECTIONS (Dateline to kum) _ Problems with voter
rolls, registration and Zimbabwean election monitors seem to bode
ill for the hotly contested parliamentary elections to be held on
Saturday and Sunday. By Henri E. Cauvin.
</P>
<P>
   AIDS-U.N. (Paris) _ A new U.N. study shows that AIDS is moving
from urban to rural areas, where victims who become too weak to
till land do not find the support services available in cities. By
Donald G. McNeil Jr.
</P>
