u f BC-SYRIA-INTERNET-$ADV26     06-23 0870
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SYRIA-INTERNET-$ADV26-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    INTERNET WINDS ITS WAY INTO SYRIAN CONSCIENCE
 &HT;    With Photo.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (f) Financial categories.
 &HT;    For Use Mon., June 26 And Thereafter.
 &HT;    By LARRY KAPLOW 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
