   CoxNet HEALTHY LIVING 0620 -- Weekend Warrior Season is in full
swing, that time of year when cooped-up big boys and girls suddenly
burst onto tennis courts, ball fields, golf courses and bicycle
lanes. And the time of year when doctors, physical therapists,
athletic trainers, chiropractors and even acupuncturists tend to
