<P>
   BRITAIN-SPEER _ LONDON _ There is a play currently running here
based on the story of Albert Speer, Adolf Hitler's armaments
minister and the well-known author of several books about his
experience in the Third Reich. The play is interesting because of
the issues it raises about Speer's role in the Nazi regime, as well
as its portrayal of Hitler as a charismatic leader. (Roughton, Cox
News Service). WITH PHOTO. MOVED TUESDAY.
