   (Will move in ``a'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   CUBAN-BOY (Dateline to kum) _ A federal appeals court on Friday
refused to take another look at the custody battle over Elian
Gonzalez, delivering what is likely to be the final blow to his
Miami relatives' efforts to keep him in the United States. An
injunction blocking Elian's father from taking the 6-year-old boy
home to Cuba will expire next Wednesday, the 11th U.S. Circuit
Court of Appeals said. (Summary from wires) By Rick Bragg.
