<P>
   AT&AMP;T-PRICES (Undated) _ AT&AMP;T on Friday set new prices for its
basic calling plans that trimmed some weekend rates but raised peak
weekday prices just two weeks after it backed off a price increase
that angered federal regulators and consumer groups. By Simon
Romero.
