Sprint assets. Not only that, the company has already been looking
at buying US West and Qwest in what could be a five-way deal that
includes Dutch-based KPN and KPN Qwest... Either of these deals
would be a blockbuster, valued somewhere more than $50 billion.
(Kanell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
