<P>
   LATINO ATHLETES GO FOR SUMMER OLYMPIC GOLD. The Olympic summer
games will showcase several Latino athletes who are favored to take
home gold medals. Leading the pack is diver Mark Ruiz, who has
already been described as the heir apparent to diving great Greg
Louganis. The Latino athletes traveling to Sidney, Australia, with
