<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following business
story for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs on
Saturday, June 24, and thereafter. For questions about stories,
contact Michael McGarr at the Daily News, (818) 713-3470.
</P>
<P>
   DOG-DAY (Los Angeles) _ It's a dog's life at the office.
Pets.com, the online pet supplier, sponsored ``Take Your Dog to
Work Day'' Friday, encouraging workers to bring their canine
companions to the workplace. The practice has real benefits, says
Pets.com's president, who allows dogs at the office. By Jason Z.
Cohen.
</P>
