<P>
   STYLE-HANKIES _ Handkerchiefs are fashionable again, but these
days stylish women are wearing them on their back, not tucking them
into their sleeves. That's because hanky-inspired prints and
designs are cropping up everywhere, in halter tops, pants, blouses
and dresses.(AHill, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 4. WITH PHOTOS.
