<P>
   SELF-TANNER _ If you want to practice ``safe sun,'' make certain
your tan comes out of a bottle. Unlike the telltale orangy streaks
of self-tanners in the past, today's sunless products are
effective, fast and a smart way to achieve a natural-looking faux
glow. (MJohnson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH PHOTOS.
