   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Saturday, June 24. The N.Y. Times News Service Night
Supervisor is Pat Ryan; phone: 888-346-9867 or 212-556-1927;
e-mail: patryan(at)nytimes.com.
