<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AOL, Time Warner gain shareholder approval of merger
 &HT;    By Marilyn Geewax and Matt Kempner
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Shareholders of Time Warner and America Online didn't
