Revolution in 1776, tells the story of devout family man and war
hero Benjamin Martin. Bryan Chafin, an 11-year-old Texas native,
co-stars as one of Gibson's four sons, Samuel Martin. This is
Bryan's first major film after a string of commercials and
independent movies made in central Texas. (Sung Park/Cox News
Service Photo)
</P>
