restaurant and Marketplace surveys and co-owner of the Seasonal
Table cooking school, says she doesn't eat chain fast food but will
indulge in quick takeout food from time to time. When she does, she
likes something delicious and nurturing. Berk, enjoying a pizza
from Frankie and Johnnie's in Brentwood. (Gus Ruelas/The Los
Angeles Daily News)
