Six years after Hans Nilsson set out to develop a research and
development center in Greater Boston for Astra AB, the Swedish
pharmaceutical company is now aiming to become a major player in
drug discovery. Inside AstraZeneca PLC's research and development
labs, from left: Peter Doig, Nilsson and Stephen Marmor talk shop.
(Bill Greene/The Boston Globe)
