<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-23 22:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3513 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-GEN-KEISSER-COLUMN-LA     06-23 1056
